\p
\v 1 In the year¦285229 \add ≈that King¦285232 Uzziyah died\add*, I saw¦285234 my master¦285237 sitting¦285238 on a tall, elevated throne¦285241, and his \add ≈long robe¦285244 covered the temple¦285248 floor\add*.\x + \xo 6:1: \xt 2Ki 15:7; 2Ch 26:23.\x*
