\v 4 Whenever one of them spoke, the sound¦285291 of their voices¦285291 make the doorways shake, and¦285293 the \add ≈temple\add* was filled¦285294 with smoke¦285295,\x + \xo 6:4: \xt Rev 15:8.\x*
