\v 5 \add ≈Yes,\add* \add *they've\add* \add ≈plotted together\add* against¦285565 you¦285565, saying,
\v 6 “Let's go up against Yehudah¦285575 \add together\add* and terrify her. Let's break¦285577 into her and crown Taveal's son as king \add right there\add* in¦285575 the middle of her.” ’
