\v 21 In those days, a \add ≈farmer\add* will preserve¦285800 a \add single,\add* young cow alive¦285800, and a couple of sheep¦285807.
\v 22 \add However,\add* because they'll produce so much milk¦285812, they'll produce yoghurt, because everyone¦285820 left in¦285823 the \add ≈country\add* will eat yoghurt and¦285809 honey¦285818.
