\v 7 so therefore¦285970 my master¦285972 will send the waters¦285977 of a large, powerful river¦285978 onto them: the Assyrian king¦285983 and¦285970 all his \add ≈majestic power\add*. It'll come like a flood filling all the channels¦285995 then¦285970 overflowing all its banks¦286001.
\v 8 It will sweep¦286003 across Yehudah¦286004, flooding yet moving on¦286004 until it reaches¦286010 your neck. It's \add ≈edges\add* will cover your entire \add ≈country\add*, Immanuel¦286018.”
\q1
\v 9 Raise the war cry, peoples¦286023, and be \add ≈terrified\add*,
\q1 and \add ≈listen¦286025\add*, all you distant¦286027 places¦286027 in the world.
