\v 2 Yahweh¦289367 told Yeshayah \add (Isaiah¦289369,\add* Amots' son), “Take off the sackcloth¦289376 and the sandals¦289379 \add ≈that you've been wearing\add*.” \add ≈So he started\add* walking¦289385 around naked¦289386\f + \fr 20:2 \ft This doesn't necessarily mean that he wore absolutely nothing.\f* and barefoot¦289387.
