\v 4 It's a sign that the Assyrian king¦289411 will lead away captives¦289416 from Egypt and Ethiopia—young¦289422 men and old, barefoot¦289425 and naked¦289424 with their buttocks¦289427 exposed—to Egypt's¦289417 shame.
\v 5 They'll be discouraged¦289431 and ashamed¦289432 \add ≈because of\add* their \add unfounded\add* confidence¦289434 in Ethiopia and their boasting¦289438 about Egypt¦289437.
