\v 14 \add ≈So¦289903 now,\add* Commander-in-chief Yahweh¦289918 has revealed¦289903 \add ≈to me\add*: ‘You all won't be \add ≈forgiven\add* for that \add ≈wickedness\add* until¦289914 you die¦289916.’
