\v 21 and I'll¦290005 put your robe and sash¦290007 on him, and give him the authority¦290009 \add ≈that you had\add*. He'll be like a father¦290014 to those who live in Yerushalem¦290016 \add (Jerusalem)\add* and \add right across\add* Yehudah¦290018 \add (Judah)\add*.
