\p \add ≈Cry loudly\add*, \add ≈you\add* ships¦290092 from Tarshish¦290093 because¦290094 your home \add port\add* has been destroyed. It's been \add ≈reported\add* to them from Kittim¦290100 \add (Cyprus¦290100 )\add*.
\v 2 Be silent¦290105 \add ≈you who live along\add* the coast¦290107, you traders¦290108 from Tsidon \add (Sidon¦290109)\add* who cross the ocean to be filled¦290112.
