\v 12 \add ≈But¦294217\add* the \add ≈negotiator\add* \add ≈replied\add*, “\add Do¦294218 you think that\add* my master sent me to \add ≈give this message\add* \add just\add* to you and your master? \add ≈Don't¦294231 you think that it's also for\add* the men¦294234 sitting¦294235 on the wall \add who'll have to\add* \add ≈join you in\add* eating their \add own\add* dung and drinking¦294244 their \add own\add* urine?”
