\v 1 \add ≈When\add* King¦294455 Hezkiyah heard¦294454 \add <the report\add*, he torn his clothes¦294460 \add too\add*, and covered¦294461 himself¦294461 with sackcloth¦294462 and went¦294463 into Yahweh's¦294465 \add ≈residence\add*.
