\v 6 \add *he\add* told them to tell their master¦294562, “Yahweh¦294566 says¦294565 not to be afraid¦294569 because of the words¦294571 that¦294572 you¦294573 heard¦294573 when the Assyrian king's servants¦294576 insulted me.
\v 7 Listen, I'll put a spirit¦294585 in him and he'll hear¦294586 a report¦294587 \add that he needs\add* to return¦294588 to his own \add ≈country\add*, and then \add ≈I'll cause him to be assassinated at home\add*.”
