\p
\v 8 Then¦294596 the \add Assyrian\add* \add ≈negotiator\add* returned¦294596 \add to find\add* the Assyrian king¦294603 because¦294609 he'd heard¦294610 that he had left¦294612 Lakish, and¦294596 he found¦294600 him fighting¦294605 against Livnah.
