\v 10 “Tell Yehudah's¦294641 King¦294639 Hezkiyah: don't¦294643 let your god¦294646 that you trust¦294649 in, deceive¦294645 you by telling \add <you\add* that Yerushalem¦294654 won't¦294643 be \add ≈conquered by\add* the Assyrian king.
