\v 14 Hezkiyah \add ≈accepted\add* the letter¦294710 brought by the messengers¦294712 and read it. Then¦294706 he went into Yahweh's¦294716 \add ≈residence\add* and spread¦294717 it out in front¦294719 of Yahweh
