\v 21 Then¦294824 Amots' son Yeshayah sent¦294824 this message to \add King\add* Hezkiyah: “Yisrael's god¦294837 Yahweh¦294836 says¦294835 that because you¦294840 prayed¦294840 to me about the Assyrian King Sennacherib¦294844,
