\p
\v 36 Then Yahweh's¦295094 messenger¦295093 went¦295091 out and \add ≈killed\add* 185,000 Assyrian \add ≈soldiers\add*—\add ≈when\add* \add @the others\add* got up early¦295102 \add the next\add* morning¦295103, wow, there were corpses¦295106 \add all around\add*!
