\v 3 “Oh Yahweh¦295182, please remember¦295183 how I've¦295188 \add ≈served you faithfully¦295190 and with integrity\add*, and done¦295195 \add ≈what pleases you\add*.” Then¦295180 Hezkiyah \add ≈cried and cried\add*.
\p
