\q1
\v 16 My master¦295396, people¦295398 live by \add ?≈such things\add*,
\q1 and my spirit \add ?≈finds life in\add* all of them.
\q1 \add ≈Please\add* restore¦295404 my health¦295404 and preserve¦295405 my life.
